{
  "video_id": "I0Nq0SnZhW8",
  "title": "When does \"bribery\" become a crime?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6280.0,
      "end_time": 10629.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk today about bribery law here in California."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10630.0,
      "end_time": 12340.0,
      "text": "And just by way of background, I&#39;m"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12340.0,
      "end_time": 15900.0,
      "text": "a former prosecutor, now a criminal defense attorney."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15900.0,
      "end_time": 18950.0,
      "text": "We represent people in California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18950.0,
      "end_time": 22410.0,
      "text": "a lot of public officials who are accused of bribery"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22410.0,
      "end_time": 24560.0,
      "text": "and a lot of individuals who are accused"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24560.0,
      "end_time": 27759.0,
      "text": "of offering or trying to make bribes."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27760.0,
      "end_time": 31500.0,
      "text": "Now the legal definition of bribery in California"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31500.0,
      "end_time": 34320.0,
      "text": "is when you offer something of value"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34320.0,
      "end_time": 37600.0,
      "text": "with the corrupt intent to influence somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37600.0,
      "end_time": 40710.0,
      "text": "in their action, vote, or opinion"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40710.0,
      "end_time": 43960.0,
      "text": "in any public or official capacity."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43960.0,
      "end_time": 45800.0,
      "text": "So, for example, this could include"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45800.0,
      "end_time": 49669.0,
      "text": "bribing a judge or a juror to decide in your favor."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49670.0,
      "end_time": 52420.0,
      "text": "It could be offering money to a county supervisor"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52420.0,
      "end_time": 56140.0,
      "text": "to vote for certain legislation that you&#39;re sponsoring."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56140.0,
      "end_time": 59410.0,
      "text": "It could be bribing a building inspector"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59410.0,
      "end_time": 62279.0,
      "text": "to sign off on your development plans."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62280.0,
      "end_time": 64280.0,
      "text": "And the important thing to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64280.0,
      "end_time": 66730.0,
      "text": "is that the crime of bribery takes"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66730.0,
      "end_time": 69650.0,
      "text": "place whenever a deal is made."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69650.0,
      "end_time": 72630.0,
      "text": "Whenever there&#39;s an offer or an acceptance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72630.0,
      "end_time": 76460.0,
      "text": "even if no money is ultimately exchanged."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76460.0,
      "end_time": 79550.0,
      "text": "So, for example, suppose that I offer my city councilman"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79550.0,
      "end_time": 82960.0,
      "text": "$10,000 cash if he votes in favor of my development"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82960.0,
      "end_time": 83979.0,
      "text": "project."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83980.0,
      "end_time": 85970.0,
      "text": "And he agrees to the deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85970.0,
      "end_time": 88390.0,
      "text": "But for some reason, I canceled the project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88400.0,
      "end_time": 90700.0,
      "text": "and I ultimately never pay him the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90700.0,
      "end_time": 93250.0,
      "text": "and he never casts a vote on the project."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93250.0,
      "end_time": 95950.0,
      "text": "He and I could still be charged with bribery"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95950.0,
      "end_time": 99960.0,
      "text": "because I offered that bribe, and he accepted that bribe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99960.0,
      "end_time": 102820.0,
      "text": "even though the deal never actually went through."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102820.0,
      "end_time": 104536.0,
      "text": "Now bribery is a felony."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104537.0,
      "end_time": 106120.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re convicted, you could face up"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106120.0,
      "end_time": 107980.0,
      "text": "to several years in custody."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107980.0,
      "end_time": 110180.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a public official, it almost certainly"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 110180.0,
      "end_time": 111940.0,
      "text": "would be the end of your political"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111940.0,
      "end_time": 114900.0,
      "text": "or sort of public service career."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114900.0,
      "end_time": 116150.0,
      "text": "And it would be a red flag on your record"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116150.0,
      "end_time": 118570.0,
      "text": "that would probably make it very difficult to obtain"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 118570.0,
      "end_time": 121330.0,
      "text": "jobs and benefits in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121330.0,
      "end_time": 124840.0,
      "text": "So to the extent that you are investigated for bribery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124840.0,
      "end_time": 127794.0,
      "text": "accused of bribery, charged with bribery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127794.0,
      "end_time": 129210.0,
      "text": "you want to do everything that you"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 129210.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134360.0,
      "text": "can now to avoid conviction and keep this off your record."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 134360.0,
      "end_time": 136670.0,
      "text": "Now the good news is that here at Shouse Law Group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136670.0,
      "end_time": 139359.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve had a great record of success in representing"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139360.0,
      "end_time": 142240.0,
      "text": "both public officials and private individuals who"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142240.0,
      "end_time": 144230.0,
      "text": "are charged with bribery."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144230.0,
      "end_time": 145850.0,
      "text": "It may be that it&#39;s all a mistake"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 145850.0,
      "end_time": 149920.0,
      "text": "and there was really no intent to do anything wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 149920.0,
      "end_time": 152519.0,
      "text": "You may have been acting entirely in good faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 152520.0,
      "end_time": 155650.0,
      "text": "It may be that the authorities entrapped you"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 155650.0,
      "end_time": 160200.0,
      "text": "into some sort of bribery exchange."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160200.0,
      "end_time": 163410.0,
      "text": "It may be that you&#39;re the victim of a false accusation."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 163410.0,
      "end_time": 165460.0,
      "text": "And unfortunately, this is an area"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 165460.0,
      "end_time": 169140.0,
      "text": "where a lot of police and investigators and prosecutors"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 169140.0,
      "end_time": 173670.0,
      "text": "are very over zealous, where they&#39;re politically motivated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173670.0,
      "end_time": 177480.0,
      "text": "where they&#39;re out to get people for improper, vindictive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 177480.0,
      "end_time": 179179.0,
      "text": "political reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 179180.0,
      "end_time": 182700.0,
      "text": "So ultimately, a lot of innocent people get charged."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 182700.0,
      "end_time": 184980.0,
      "text": "A lot of cases get filed that shouldn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 184980.0,
      "end_time": 186709.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s where we come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 186710.0,
      "end_time": 188640.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re in this situation, call us."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 188640.0,
      "end_time": 191339.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll see what we can do to help you."
    }
  ]
}